Capital Markets

Company Overview of Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited operates as a full service investment banking firm. The company offers equities, fixed income, commodities, and investment banking services. It also provides broker, dealer, and asset management services. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is based in London, the United Kingdom. Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited operates as a subsidiary of Jefferies Holdings II Limited.


Vintners Place68 Upper Thames StreetLondon,  EC4V 3BJUnited KingdomFounded in 2000










