Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited Key Developments

Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited Announce Resignation of David Weaver as Director
Jun 7 16
Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited announced that Mr. David Weaver has resigned as Director with effect from May 31, 2016.


Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited Announces Resignation of Timothy Barker Effective from March 31, 2016
Apr 1 16
Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited announced that Mr. Timothy Barker has resigned with effect from March 31, 2016.


Marc Bailey Resigns as Director of Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited
Jul 31 15
The Board of Jefferies International (Holdings) Limited announced that Marc Bailey has resigned as Director with effect from 31 July 2015.


